{"type":"message","id":"a9d0c4f6","parentId":"dad7d19e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:50:21.066Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个搜索结果页面内容太多太杂乱了。让我换一个方式，直接用更专业的搜索关键词来获取更精准的信息。我需要搜索4个主题：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2026 趋势\n2. 智能安防 2026 发展趋势  \n3. 网络系统集成 2026 市场动态\n4. IT运维服务 AIOps 2026 行业趋势\n\n让我逐一搜索这些主题。","thinkingSignature":"0d96734e12b0577c6a3fc0c95384dd31d24b3b0da51d00d331f21f2855a6e3c2"},{"type":"text","text":"搜索结果太杂乱了。让我关闭浏览器，然后用更精准的方式搜索。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3mum6j82dmgs_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"close","targetId":"E4AF04FE34BF4C98C7B8717B6F3AECD5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":48090,"output":158,"cacheRead":30670,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78918,"cost":{"input":0.014426999999999999,"output":0.0001896,"cacheRead":0.0009200999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015536699999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773935414213}}
